Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.60,0:01:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是本田透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.47,0:01:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈过世后已经一年半了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.78,0:01:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.18,0:01:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但仍能像这样感受到这蓝天白云及徐徐微风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.18,0:01:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种幸福的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.62,0:01:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许是草摩家的所有人常陪伴在身旁所赐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.99,0:01:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的妈呀!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.09,0:01:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,底…纸袋的底破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.53,0:01:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕 我来帮你捡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.77,0:01:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎么好意思麻烦你这位素昧平生的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.37,0:01:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系 人有困难时应该互相帮助啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.27,0:01:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 真抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.74,0:02:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是个超会给周遭找麻烦的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.48,0:02:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.38,0:02:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我光是呼吸都会给人造成困扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.22,0:02:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,纸袋之所以会破就是在警告我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.96,0:02:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不该如此厚脸皮跑去紫吴哥家拜访
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.16,0:02:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇!!对不起!!我跟全世界的人道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.87,0:02:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不该来拜访的！对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.84,0:02:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是…利津吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.11,0:02:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的妈呀!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.01,0:02:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,素昧平生的人居然知道我的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.91,0:02:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可见我早就恶名昭彰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.02,0:02:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我却毫不知情还活得这么悠栽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.82,0:02:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.29,0:02:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也向跟我同名的人说声对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.62,0:02:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.46,0:02:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.49,0:02:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利津的登场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.06,0:02:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是难得啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.36,0:02:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,个性软弱的利津会主动来找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.47,0:03:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.54,0:03:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在您家门口给小透添了麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.67,0:03:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 一点也不麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.11,0:03:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很高兴认识你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.08,0:03:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利津
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.15,0:03:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是女性吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.52,0:03:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.05,0:03:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利津是我以前在温泉旅馆时受到照顾的老板娘之女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.36,0:03:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你跟老板娘长得太像了 所以我一眼就认出你来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.60,0:03:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想起来了 利津是十二生肖的猴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.94,0:03:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实我的孩子也是被十二生肖的猴怪所附身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.61,0:03:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是利津为何突然跑来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.11,0:03:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 造成你的困扰了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.18,0:03:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.89,0:03:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,骗你的啦 跟你开玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的个性跟你妈还真像呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.22,0:03:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都快出社会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.76,0:03:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为人处世得学着稳重点才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.36,0:04:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.76,0:04:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次见面 我叫草摩利津
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.77,0:04:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前些日子家母承蒙你的照顾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.04,0:04:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里 我才是呢 我叫本田透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.37,0:04:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 这是我的点心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.74,0:04:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么 送我的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.14,0:04:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.94,0:04:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本来想买水果送你们但又不知道你们爱吃什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.38,0:04:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以决定买水果的书送你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.25,0:04:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么 对不起 你不喜欢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一点也不会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.42,0:04:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起!原谅我!!我马上去买水果!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.39,0:04:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.66,0:04:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系 你就坦白跟我说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.47,0:04:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我果然是个没资格来你家拜访的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.60,0:04:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都说了没这回事的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.11,0:04:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是嘛 我真的好想认识你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.34,0:04:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以说你来家里玩 我是真的真的很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.08,0:04:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.15,0:05:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是从家母那边听说你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.56,0:05:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以好想见你一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.49,0:05:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不好意思 不过还是很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.66,0:05:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笑起来更是个大美女啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.30,0:05:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,家里有客人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.07,0:05:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希好久不见了 对不起 打扰你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.87,0:05:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是那身打扮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.24,0:05:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.24,0:05:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我马上脱掉就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.28,0:05:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果真还是那副德性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.72,0:05:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利津 你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.02,0:05:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去泡茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.49,0:05:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你别忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.09,0:05:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.13,0:05:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难得利津能鼓起勇气来找我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就对她好一点嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利津是来见小透的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.34,0:05:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.01,0:05:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不见了 虽然上次见过伯母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.44,0:05:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道她近况还好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.18,0:05:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 她很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.31,0:05:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看起来也不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.55,0:06:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.38,0:06:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希愈看愈像阿绫哥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.12,0:06:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你慢坐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.99,0:06:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不是说了不该说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.89,0:06:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 我就是话多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.69,0:06:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在不自觉的情况下给周遭人带来不悦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.63,0:06:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.60,0:06:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然没错！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.03,0:06:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 让大家感到不悦 我马上失陪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.74,0:06:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 打扰了这么久 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.01,0:06:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么行呢 你才刚来啊 怎么可以走呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.71,0:06:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我还没招呼你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.85,0:06:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这怎么敢当 请你别这么客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.92,0:06:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 是我自己想招待你 你再坐一会儿嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.15,0:06:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说我哪承当得起呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.06,0:06:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到你这么说我就心满意足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.42,0:06:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又何必这么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.79,0:06:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.49,0:06:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.40,0:06:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 你有没有受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.06,0:06:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没事 倒是利津她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.47,0:06:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我居然在别人家里打破茶杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.11,0:06:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我简直是恶魔的化身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.27,0:06:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 是我打破的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.34,0:07:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 我不该来拜访
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.05,0:07:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我道歉 我跟全世界的人道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.58,0:07:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利津 危险！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.09,0:07:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为…为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.79,0:07:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你明明是女生 为何会变身…呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.49,0:07:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇咧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,血…血！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.87,0:07:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.87,0:07:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪 耶～？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.20,0:07:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此 小透受伤了 有空就过来看看她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚上去也行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.44,0:07:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么 奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.38,0:07:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟今天怎么这么好说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.45,0:07:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该不会偷偷爱上小透了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.72,0:07:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被我猜中了吗 你好坏 好死相喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.62,0:07:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的有够白痴的 我懒得跟你说啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.09,0:07:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是说利津是个男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.73,0:07:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但从以前就男扮女装舍弃男儿身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.40,0:08:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此啊 我还认定她是女生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.24,0:08:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 包扎好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.11,0:08:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.61,0:08:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是他为何要男扮女装呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.31,0:08:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他说男扮女装感觉上比较安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.98,0:08:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看利津就知道他很内向吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.52,0:08:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果打扮成男生看起来会更没魄力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.45,0:08:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.22,0:08:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 利津人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.16,0:08:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 上帝 神明 请惩罚我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.47,0:08:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利津！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.73,0:08:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危…危险啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他什么时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.50,0:08:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道这种事不是道歉就能了事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害你受重伤真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.98,0:08:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有受重伤 只是小擦伤罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.85,0:08:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不敢说出自己是男儿身这件事也要跟你道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.42,0:08:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我实在很丢脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.38,0:08:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.75,0:08:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么 原来他也知道丢脸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.95,0:08:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得一点也不丢脸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且还很适合你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.33,0:09:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 这种安慰话好像有点画蛇添足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.10,0:09:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我为何…为什么老是闯祸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.47,0:09:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老给周遭人制造困扰、带来麻烦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.34,0:09:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 也不是现在才发生这种状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.17,0:09:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这样的人活在世上到底有什么意义呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.81,0:09:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 我是个毫无用处的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.38,0:09:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然还死皮赖脸的活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.65,0:09:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真恨这样的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.59,0:09:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干脆…干脆…像我这种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.46,0:09:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本不配活在这个世界上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.96,0:09:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我又没那个勇气…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是不需要的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.80,0:09:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本不需要那种勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人就是因为活着…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.37,0:09:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为活着才会有喜怒哀乐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.38,0:09:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能出生到这个世上也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.09,0:10:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利津！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脚扭到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.44,0:10:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是有够死皮赖脸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.94,0:10:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,随便你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.91,0:10:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.64,0:10:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只听说小透受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.41,0:10:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 真抱歉 波鸟哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.58,0:10:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之 发生了许多事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.59,0:10:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的伤呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是手擦伤罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.99,0:10:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且由希已经帮我包扎 没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.40,0:10:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.66,0:10:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 还让你专程来一趟 真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你的关心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.94,0:10:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.27,0:10:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以的话我想在这里过夜 不知道可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.75,0:10:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是难得啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.98,0:11:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到你今天会说出这么积极的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.82,0:11:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 我只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么利津跟波鸟会在家里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.79,0:11:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.83,0:11:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这样过了三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.23,0:11:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利津常好像想说什么似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.40,0:11:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但终究还是什么话也没说 每天只知道发呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.34,0:11:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盐巴的量可以吗 会不会太咸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.58,0:11:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 刚刚好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.35,0:11:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.08,0:11:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不错吧 羡慕吧 我的新婚妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.19,0:11:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.75,0:11:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继续这么胡扯下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.26,0:11:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当心被踢到屋顶去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌 你也在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.16,0:11:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁是谁的新婚妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再不闭上你的烂嘴 当心我扭断你的脖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.83,0:11:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈呀 阿夹好凶喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.07,0:11:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,气死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.84,0:11:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安 阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.84,0:11:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你别只会笑 要懂得拒绝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.97,0:11:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.17,0:12:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就因为这样 那个白痴才会得寸进尺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.31,0:12:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说些五四三的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.91,0:12:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因妒忌而迁怒 实在太逊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.68,0:12:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.22,0:12:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟 你为何还在这里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.55,0:12:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为波鸟在此 利津的伤势才康复得这么快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这件事跟我无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.36,0:12:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么 牛奶没了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.49,0:12:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真抱歉 没了吗 我马上去买
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.83,0:12:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 不用这么麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.67,0:12:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那怎么行呢 厨房一切由我负责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.07,0:12:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我却犯这么大的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的 非常对…对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.41,0:12:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.34,0:12:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我早上都吃玉米片加牛奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.38,0:12:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才把阿夹的牛奶给喝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.45,0:12:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯罪的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罪大恶极的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.38,0:12:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你尽管惩罚我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.82,0:12:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你惩罚我吧～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.86,0:12:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对喔 你也还在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.99,0:12:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 因为我拜托紫吴哥让我住这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.26,0:12:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且本来只说住一晚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.80,0:12:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却两晚、三晚一天天增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.33,0:12:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不但如此早上还吃玉米片加牛奶 真是任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利津
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.33,0:13:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利津 拜托你别端着牛奶跑好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.11,0:13:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请别客气 这盘牛奶给你喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.48,0:13:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死都不喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.71,0:13:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我到底该如何是好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.05,0:13:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只需马上去买瓶牛奶回来就行了 白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.45,0:13:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.62,0:13:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希 今天睡过头了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害你睡过头了 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.16,0:13:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害你迟到了 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.53,0:13:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么会这样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.63,0:13:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为迟到的关系害你被退学 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.13,0:13:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 我早就教过你了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.17,0:13:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正义永远会赢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.24,0:13:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁是正义来着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.78,0:13:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就某个角度而言紫吴也是恶魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.05,0:13:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都说了 凡事学着沉着稳重点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.68,0:13:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家并不会特别在意你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.72,0:13:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你老跟大家道歉 大家也很困扰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.22,0:13:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是老样子 这么残酷的话也能轻松脱口而出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.63,0:14:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也想当个堂堂男子汉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.33,0:14:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然 我好想有一天能像阿绫哥那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.04,0:14:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是不可能的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.37,0:14:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么 这是无法达成的梦想吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.41,0:14:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为阿绫的自信心超出人类的常规
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.41,0:14:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先不提绫女的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.91,0:14:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之 周遭人不像你想像中的那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.22,0:14:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会责骂你也不会怪你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.75,0:14:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多给自己一点空间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.39,0:14:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.89,0:14:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对…我想说的就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少瞎掰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.46,0:14:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 请原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.57,0:14:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 请原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.57,0:14:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 对不起 爸 妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.92,0:14:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利津
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.18,0:14:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我笑得那么甜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.49,0:15:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我老觉得他在责怪自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.53,0:15:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如同由希跟阿夹那样 还有其他的草摩家人那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.46,0:15:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不断责怪自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.03,0:15:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到底是为了什么活在这个世上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.34,0:15:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.04,0:15:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真高兴有生下小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.58,0:15:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为有小透 我才能每天都活得这么开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.88,0:15:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么我是为了见妈妈才出生到人世间来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.62,0:15:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是这样就开心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.93,0:15:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要！不要！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.23,0:15:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 原谅我 你饶了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.70,0:15:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我马上买新的章鱼烧来 你饶了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.17,0:15:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 我不该拿回来的 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.57,0:15:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.61,0:15:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟世上的所有人道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.81,0:15:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利津…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.14,0:15:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说紫吴吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.35,0:15:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.25,0:16:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他说不吃章鱼烧就没有灵感写小说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.28,0:16:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.02,0:16:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.39,0:16:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.63,0:16:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 小透你想说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.10,0:16:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系 你先说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.26,0:16:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那怎么行呢 你先说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.70,0:16:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎么好意思先说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.93,0:16:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.07,0:16:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继续这么客套下去可能谁都别想说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.47,0:16:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以说还是你先说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.88,0:16:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.98,0:16:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有事想请问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.95,0:16:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你上次和家母见面时有没有听说些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.89,0:16:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比如说觉得我让她感到丢脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.33,0:16:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真抱歉 我这么问你 你也会感到很困扰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.10,0:16:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都怪我这个儿子不肖 害她这么抬不起头来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.17,0:16:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自己也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.10,0:16:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是个没出息的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.44,0:17:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然被附身了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.58,0:17:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但又不像其他十二生肖的人那么有才华
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.85,0:17:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是在运动或课业上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.62,0:17:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不比别人多付出一倍以上的努力就会跟不上大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.52,0:17:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 真抱歉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到草摩家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.06,0:17:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然出了我这种耻辱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.59,0:17:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为此父母只能不断跟大家道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.13,0:17:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当我发现到只要男扮女装就会感到安心点时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.33,0:17:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就开始男扮女装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.80,0:17:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但没想到却因此害父母增加跟人道歉的次数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.08,0:17:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直想振作起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.08,0:17:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也想恢复男儿身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.82,0:17:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但还是没有自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.66,0:17:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就因这样才更不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.59,0:17:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的胸口有如针扎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.77,0:18:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实爸妈也不想跟人道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.30,0:18:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们多想有个不会害他们老跟人磕头道歉的儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.37,0:18:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能有个好儿子就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.98,0:18:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.28,0:18:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说不定没有我还比较好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.19,0:18:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出生的存在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.89,0:18:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是没有意义的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.73,0:18:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算相信是有意义的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.97,0:18:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却也一点一点遗失了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.54,0:18:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我却仍赖活着 实在有够死皮赖脸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.68,0:18:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定可以找得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.21,0:18:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出为何会出生的意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.22,0:18:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用自己的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.75,0:18:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为…因为事实上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.03,0:19:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想世上应该没有人一开始就知道自己为何会出生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.10,0:19:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.31,0:19:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都得靠自己的力量去寻找这个答案吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.41,0:19:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何会出生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.05,0:19:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何会活着 绝对有它存在的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.42,0:19:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想这些都得靠自己去寻找出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.72,0:19:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比方说活在梦想、工作、人群中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.16,0:19:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己寻找答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.43,0:19:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听起来或许很暧昧不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.67,0:19:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也可能会因此失去某些东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.97,0:19:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但还是希望知道原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.21,0:19:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要还活着 我也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.11,0:19:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且能的话 我希望能走进人群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.69,0:20:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从别人身上寻找到这个意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.06,0:20:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了别人而活的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.09,0:20:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望别人能对我说他愿意接纳我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.83,0:20:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有时也会觉得很沮丧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.00,0:20:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我会继续加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.47,0:20:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.71,0:20:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以无所谓的 就算死皮赖脸也无妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.78,0:20:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为 人能死皮赖脸的活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.72,0:20:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,表示他活得很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.56,0:20:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好想再听一次这番话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.10,0:20:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好希望你再说一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.94,0:20:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像这样的我也能找到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.21,0:20:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何会活着的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.44,0:21:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能找到就好了 我想迟早应该能找到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.95,0:21:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且也希望自己有朝一日能为别人而活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.52,0:21:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能跟那个人一起吃章鱼烧那就更开心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.33,0:21:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.40,0:21:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有朝一日 想跟某个人一起吃章鱼烧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.20,0:21:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也希望能说出自己是为了谁而出生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.18,0:21:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而这句话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.61,0:21:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有某人等着我跟他说那就更好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.89,0:21:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得赶快把章鱼烧带回去给紫吴哥吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.19,0:21:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.06,0:21:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴哥说一吃章鱼烧就会变身为战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.96,0:21:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.90,0:21:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用章鱼烧的那股力量…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.60,0:21:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？

